## Key Results

### Vehicle Category Reachability

| Category | Reached | Success Rate |
|----------|---------|-------------|
| Truck | 17/17 | 100% |
| Bus | 17/17 | 100% |
| Car/Microbus | 15/17 | 88% |
| Rickshaw/Van/Bike | 13/17 | 76% |

### Case Comparison (Core Result)

| Metric | Case 1 (Source) | Case 2 (Current-pos) | **Case 3 (Pool)** |
|--------|:-:|:-:|:-:|
| Avg iterations | 100.0 | 100.0 | **23.9 (−76%)** |
| Avg time (ms) | 3.295 | 3.674 | **0.606 (−82%)** |
| Avg energy proxy | 0.0033 | 0.0037 | **0.0006 (−82%)** |
| Avg final cost | 501.83 | 1208.17 | 542.33 |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Case 3 (pool-based) achieves 5.4× faster response time and 76% fewer iterations** than standard rerouting, with only ~8% cost increase over Case 1. This supports the hypothesis.

