## Verification

- **Compilation**: `g++ -std=c++17 -O2` — success ✅
- **Execution**: Exit code 0, all output files generated ✅
- **Case comparison**: Case 3 shows expected reduction in iterations/time ✅
- **Reproducibility**: Random seed 42, deterministic results ✅

## How to Run

```bash
cd e:\akhand_sir_research_topic\dorkari\weekly_update_11
python generate_dataset.py                    # Generate input data
g++ -std=c++17 -O2 -o vehicle_pool_planner.exe vehicle_pool_planner.cpp
.\vehicle_pool_planner.exe > output.txt 2>&1  # Run full pipeline
```
